      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HY FILANTE (5) settled close to the pace and finished well but could only manage second last start over 1800m at this track, that effort coming on the back of a sound third at Port Pirie the run before. Finds a suitable assignment and can play a significant role. TREACHEROUS ROCK (6) went back last start then worked home in good style to finish 1.4 metres from the winner in second at this track over 1800m, that effort following a eighth at this track the run prior. Meets a comparable field and he can find winning ways. SHIRLEY NOT (9) is in the mix following a fourth at her most recent appearance over 1800m at this track. Last-start placegetter AMYS BABY ANGEL (1) has improved with each start this time in and is well served by this draw.",
